    <content type="html"><![CDATA[<h1 id="Hexo主题Yilia添加网站浏览量统计"><a href="#Hexo主题Yilia添加网站浏览量统计" class="headerlink" title="Hexo主题Yilia添加网站浏览量统计"></a>Hexo主题Yilia添加网站浏览量统计</h1><h2 id="方式"><a href="#方式" class="headerlink" title="方式"></a>方式</h2><p>这里使用不蒜子的脚本统计</p><h2 id="操作步骤"><a href="#操作步骤" class="headerlink" title="操作步骤"></a>操作步骤</h2><p>首先去<a href="http://busuanzi.ibruce.info/" target="_blank" rel="noopener">不蒜子官网</a>复制以下代码</p><figure class="highlight plain"><table><tr><td class="gutter"><pre><span class="line">1</span><br></pre></td><td class="code"><pre><span class="line">&lt;script async src&#x3D;&quot;&#x2F;&#x2F;busuanzi.ibruce.info&#x2F;busuanzi&#x2F;2.3&#x2F;busuanzi.pure.mini.js&quot;&gt;&lt;&#x2F;script&gt;</span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure><p>打开自己的blog本地仓库路径</p><a id="more"></a><figure class="highlight taggerscript"><table><tr><td class="gutter"><pre><span class="line">1</span><br></pre></td><td class="code"><pre><span class="line">hexo<span class="symbol">\t</span>hemes<span class="symbol">\y</span>ilia<span class="symbol">\l</span>ayout_partial<span class="symbol">\f</span>ooter.ejs</span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure><p>在footer.ejs文件最后粘贴此行代码，将脚本添加至自己的博客项目中。</p><p>然后根据个人喜好添加以下代码</p><blockquote><p><strong>本站总访问量</strong></p><figure class="highlight plain"><table><tr><td class="gutter"><pre><span class="line">1</span><br><span class="line">2</span><br><span class="line">3</span><br></pre></td><td class="code"><pre><span class="line">&lt;span id&#x3D;&quot;busuanzi_container_site_pv&quot;&gt;</span><br><span class="line">    本站总访问量&lt;span id&#x3D;&quot;busuanzi_value_site_pv&quot;&gt;&lt;&#x2F;span&gt;次</span><br><span class="line">&lt;&#x2F;span&gt;</span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure><p><strong>本站访客数</strong></p><figure class="highlight plain"><table><tr><td class="gutter"><pre><span class="line">1</span><br><span class="line">2</span><br><span class="line">3</span><br></pre></td><td class="code"><pre><span class="line">&lt;span id&#x3D;&quot;busuanzi_container_site_uv&quot;&gt;</span><br><span class="line">  本站访客数&lt;span id&#x3D;&quot;busuanzi_value_site_uv&quot;&gt;&lt;&#x2F;span&gt;人次</span><br><span class="line">&lt;&#x2F;span&gt;</span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure><p><strong>本文总阅读量</strong></p><figure class="highlight plain"><table><tr><td class="gutter"><pre><span class="line">1</span><br><span class="line">2</span><br><span class="line">3</span><br></pre></td><td class="code"><pre><span class="line">&lt;span id&#x3D;&quot;busuanzi_container_page_pv&quot;&gt;</span><br><span class="line">  本文总阅读量&lt;span id&#x3D;&quot;busuanzi_value_page_pv&quot;&gt;&lt;&#x2F;span&gt;次</span><br><span class="line">&lt;&#x2F;span&gt;</span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure></blockquote>]]></content>
    
